            </hr>
              <img src="../../img/wc_solution_explorer.png" align="left"/>
             <list>
                <item><b>1.</b> Right click on the selected unversioned item(s) 
					you want to add in Solution Explorer. An item could be a file
					 directory or project. <br></br>
				</item>
			</list>
			<br clear="ALL"/>
			<br></br>
			
			 <img src="../../img/item_menu.png" align="left"/>   <br></br><br></br>                    
             <list>
                <item><b>2.</b> Select <b>add</b> from the item menu that pops up.<br></br>
				</item>
			</list>
			<br clear="ALL"/>
			<br></br>
				
			<b>3.</b> Notice that the status symbol has changed in front of the 
            item(s) added in Solution Explorer from 
            <img src="../../img/unrevisioned.png"/>
            to <img src="../../img/add.png"/>
            <br></br><br></br>
            
            I.e. after having added a file Ankh will show the file status as: 
            <br></br>
            <img src="../../img/added_file.png"/></p><br></br>
